For Sale Brand New In Box Us Optics SR8C 1-8 Scope. This has the bright daylight visible red dot and a custom Mil Scale BDC reticle designed for 3Gun competition with a BDC built in. BDC is calibrated for .223 using 77gr SMK @ 2720fps, but you can use other bullets as well I have all the BDC information to make other loads work as well. Red Dot is on the second focal plane and DOES NOT change in size as you increase the power. Also when you turn the red dot off it disappears completely, it does not have a black dot behind it to obscure the reticle. The Mil Scale reticle is on the first focal plane and DOES increase and decrease in size as you change the power of the scope. You can use the reticle like a regular Mil reticle but this one has hash marks every 0.5 mil to make ranging targets more precise. Or you can use the BDC for quick shots out to 800yds. BDC includes wind hold overs for 2.5, 5 and 10 MPH wind. The red dot is centered on the scope at the 200 yard mark. The cross hairs are above the center of the scope at the 100 yd mark. Zero the crosshairs at 100yd and you will have a 35 yd zero for your red dot. At 1 power the reticle almost disappears and the bright red dot stands out, Excellent for fast up close shooting. When you increase the power the reticle shows up nice and clear for those long shots. 
This scope comes with std zeroing knobs in 0.2 mils per click and 9.4 mils per turn.
